name: Daily life
short_description:
Everyday until my life consists of actually working for a living. I am going to make a daily life schedule. 
1. Workout every morning 8 a.m or earlier!?
2. Practice learning to play guitar
3. Learn about terminology
4. Spend an hour at the library on diff. Studies
5. Learn new vocab
6. Learn about nutrition & wellness
7. Write everything/idea down in binder
8. Take Capri for picnics & park dates
9. Work on getting a job
10. Run every evening/ Pilate's on weekends

REMAIN HAPPY, FOCUSED, AND CAREFREE! Just stay busy and never let a minute go by lying around disappointed and depressed. You have to make something of yourself! However, you are the only one capable of this task.
summary: To much time wasted this summer, time to be someone again!
